DONATE: https://tiltify.com/+esoccer-aid-for-unicef-official/ea-live-stream-and-rewards

Some of your favourite stars from the footballing and entertainment world will be taking part in the first-ever eSoccer Aid event on 27th June. 

See stars such as Robbie Williams, James McAvoy, and Sir Mo Farah battle it out against Usain Bolt, Olly Murs and Liam Payne in  EA SPORTS FIFA20 as Soccer Aid World XI FC take on England in a series of 8 1v1 matchups to decide the inaugural champions. 

Throughout the broadcast, we will be fundraising for Unicef’s work to help stop the spread of coronavirus and limit the impact on children’s lives.
